  "merge_notes": "School conflict: ICT (time-based levels) vs General SMC (pivot-based zones). Picked ICT by majority (1 ICT + 1 General; General is not a specific school, so ICT stands). Nuance: ICT rules are time-specific (midnight, 8:30 EST); SMC rules are timeframe-agnostic. Both preserved.",
